The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 19 November is 1,249,431 (2,219.8 cases per 100,000 population). In the seven days to 14 November, there were 153,873 new confirmed cases (273.4 new cases per 100,000). In the seven days to 07 November, there were 142,517 new cases and so the new cases have risen by 8% ( 11,356 extra cases).
